Ranger Help for: martial
========================

SUMMARY:
The Martial branch encompasses the Ranger's combat abilities. These
are the techniques of a warrior who fights with cunning, speed, and
knowledge of the terrain rather than brute force alone.

Key martial skills include:

  Quickshot       - Rapid archery attack, firing multiple shots
  Longshot        - Long-range bow attack reaching adjacent rooms
  Heartshot       - Carefully aimed crossbow shot to the heart
  Coordinate      - Organizes a group attack for improved effectiveness
  Ambush          - Devastating surprise attack from concealment
  Concealment     - Hides using natural camouflage
  Move Silently   - Travel without being noticed
  Set Snare       - Sets a hidden trap for the unwary
  Fortify         - Builds a defensive barricade
  Compare         - Compares weapons or armor quality
  Balance Weapon  - Improves a weapon's accuracy
  Treat Armor     - Treats leather armor for better protection

Rangers are at their deadliest when fighting in their primary terrain
against their chosen enemy species.

